\n<br />\n呢個國家究竟仲有冇尊嚴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd10be6bab440ed29aded313e2a0e36fdb8b7007","tid":1503144,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"564949a7515f4f2102b94b6d2002ee794971aa71","tid":1503144,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"岩啦，最怕你唔播，<br />\n播多仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:15:35.000Z","msg":"最好請多d外國人拍、洗多d外匯，越大制作越好"},{"pid":"9e7528ec605ef28499931b4d12ae1fdfd85c70ac","tid":1503144,"uid":283157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69625e4a2eeb763e49f7edd70407eb2b45600c41","tid":1503144,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾時拍套電影講下支那係瑞士銀行0個<span style=\"color: red;\"> 7萬8千億 </span>賄款? </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec33f866ece4c596f0bc3ba416b8cb0c683a943","tid":1503144,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e7528ec605ef28499931b4d12ae1fdfd85c70ac","tid":1503144,"uid":283157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"The day we fall, our enemies arise"},{"pid":"074adf7bb5a363f062e2577b1c741d636840d31d","tid":1503144,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2e74bb1fd046aed61e2c10bd4b2dca0e25e467","tid":1503144,"uid":109262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:13:35.000Z","msg":"利害了我的國！<br />\n要特登拍套電影來介紹<br />\n成功爭取中國國旗提早1秒喺香港升起<br />\n<br />\n呢個國家究竟仲有冇尊嚴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"那一天！1997年7月1日<br />\n<br />\n紫荊花綻放，五星紅旗飄揚，歷經百年滄桑的香港回到了祖國母親的懷抱。<br />\n<br />\n而那時，他是外交部禮賓司副司長，也是中英香港政權交接儀式籌備組的組長。為給祖國多爭取2秒，他和他的團隊與英方代表團無數次斡旋，誓讓五星紅旗在0時0分0秒準時升起！<br />\n<br />\n他就是叱吒風雲的中國資深外交家&mdash;&mdash;安文彬！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/137727232_391471/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F137727232_391471%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=f2655be5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/137727232_391471/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a><br />\n<br />\n係早兩秒呀！<br />\n<br />\n如果一個國家事無大小都有規有距堅守原則係好值得尊敬<br />\n<br />\n但中國唔係"},{"pid":"dea172fbb6a9b02708e94f97df18dfb259d8464e","tid":1503144,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5072fb9180b6c7fb9bf30a0487cf1c5b8196b7b","tid":1503144,"uid":160348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"我唔同你講廢話。睇埋呢條，大家自行定奪邊條片先代表到香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JvFqZSzTRRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJvFqZSzTRRI&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=e3d05148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JvFqZSzTRRI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"我既鄉下呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcbc177a4cd0838bcc897839cb100ac83f89c19","tid":1503144,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"十月一播返表姐你好野系列夠做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67346240d8913c59a107e2bbe14f6d3fd1830a22","tid":1503144,"uid":269623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:58:15.000Z","